overview: The doctors and staff and Barnett-Davis Dental Group are aware that their patients only have one set of adult teeth that will have to last them a lifetime. For that reason, they offer a full selection of services that range from preventive to cosmetic procedures. Drs. Marc and Kelly Barnett, Dr. Tracy Davis and Dr. Nick Matthews provide these services to patients throughout Missouri, including Rogersville and Nixa. Tooth whitening is a patient favorite that can make a huge difference in a smile that has lost its luster. At Barnett-Davis Dental Group, there is a solution for the majority of cosmetic woes that plague dental patients. A Nixa smile makeover with a cosmetic specialist is only a consultation away.
